## Defensive Cyber Security Aka Blue Teaming(Blue Team)

##Roles Key Roles
- ⛨ SOC(Security Operations Centre ) Analyst -They monitor the organisations systems/networks and hardware in real time to spot, 
  suspiscious and expected threats or normal operations/ behaviours.

- 🤺 Incident Responder -These persons will be the first to respond to the incident. If the activity is confirmed to be a threats the IR(Incident Responder) 
  has to start containing, monitoring and prevent in real time(while threat is happening) the threat actors(Black Hats) and their method of attack.
  IR(Incident Responder) will also, gather information on what,when,where and how the bad actors(Black hats/Threat Actors) breached the system/network
  with the methods, targerts(who they attacked and what they attacked)they had used, gathering this information to further help protect the organisation.

